body_html:
You cannot run 64 bit software on a 32 bit OS.
Some users had success compiling TF on 32 bit systems, but we have not.
Unfortunately, that is all I have about this issue. You may try searching for relevant issues or stackoverflow questions to see what people did to build TF on 32 bit systems.
